value.name: 1.63 m to feet and inches
value.snippet: Here you find answers to questions like: What is 1.63 m in feet and inches? To convert from meters to feet and inches, multiply the value in meter (1.63) by 3.28 to get: 1.63 m x 3.28 = 5.34777 feet . Take the decimal part of 5.34777 (0.34777) then multiply it by 12 to turn it into inches. So, 0.34777 foot x 12 = 4.17324 inches.
